      <title>Bharti Airtel 跟随 Reliance 涨价，上调印度移动套餐价格</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/bharti-raises-india-mobile-plan-prices-following-reliance-hike</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度第二大电话运营商巴帝电信有限公司 (Bharti Airtel Ltd.) 表示，将提高其移动套餐价格，此前市场领导者 Reliance Jio Infocomm Ltd. 也采取了类似举措，此举可能结束长达数年的价格战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/bharti-raises-india-mobile-plan-prices-following-reliance-hike</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 03:57:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
